data.description: Discover spacious living in this charming 3 bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom townhouse nestled on a desirable end lot. This well-appointed home offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality, featuring an open floor plan, spacious bedrooms, and extra storage in the garage, just to name a few. With a convenient location and Transitional design, it's an ideal residence for those seeking both comfort and practicality.
